    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document provides a set of requirements for Advanced Multipath in MPLS networks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Advanced Multipath is a formalization of multipath techniques currently in use in IP and MPLS networks and a set of extensions to existing multipath techniques.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
